{
  "texts": [
    "The complete API call, along with the exact prompt, the temperature, and other hyper-parameters are included in S4 Table.",
    "For both ChatGPT and LlaMA-2, we assigned 20 notes out of the 742 as our hyper-parameter and prompt tuning set.",
    "For ChatGPT, an interactive cloud-based environment (i.e playground) was utilized initially to fine-tune the prompt.",
    "After initial exploratory analysis using these 20 notes, they were scored via the API using the best prompt and hyper-parameter found in the interactive mode.",
    "For LlaMA-2, the exploration was performed locally, on the same 20 notes."
  ]
}